01:03:02.630 --> 01:03:04.677
asks in the meeting,
or are learnings.

01:03:04.677 --> 01:03:05.510
STEVEN PINKER: Asks.

01:03:05.510 --> 01:03:07.040
AUDIENCE: Asks-- yeah, plural.

